{"tid":2411472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵人交配嘅你，睇多兩本書","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T13:02:15.000Z","uid":84037,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c66b93c3dfa1181c8c2ea7906501f6c0aeefbcee","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />珍尼佛羅培茲：咩為之有水平嘅書，介紹下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：樓鼠唔係文人，水平同品味都係垃圾，純粹鳩up <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實睇吓小說都已經好好，講嘢會冇咁枯燥，用字都會順啲，想像力同創造力都會喺睇一本好小說期間滋潤到。以下介紹：<br />\n1. 兄弟 作者余華<br />\n簡單嘅文筆，生動有趣嘅小故事，唏噓不已的大主線，家庭倫理愛情道德都有講到啲，扮下有修養又得，慢慢咀嚼又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 金庸系列 <br />\n依家愈嚟愈少人睇金庸啲書，但金庸嘅武俠小說可以學到唔少嘢，睇過嘅搵機會重溫吓都得。<br />\n3. Stephen King 系列<br />\nSK啲書，英文水平唔算太難，而且成日俾人拎嚟拍電影，直接好處就係當未來有電影上，或者約人睇戲睇SK改編嘅電影，可以吹兩句「原著我睇過」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，搵一啲可以引用/應用落日常嘅書。樓鼠會推薦人物傳記<br />\n1. 唐寧街歲月<br />\n鐵娘子嘅傳記，J死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. The ride of a lifetime<br />\n一本樓鼠幾鍾意嘅傳記，前迪迪尼CEO寫嘅，唔同人睇會有唔同角度，了解去run一個壟斷性集團背後嘅決策係點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣進修吓嘅，可以睇啲popular science 嘅書，學到知識之餘，亦學到點樣深入淺出解釋一啲難明嘅概念俾人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別介紹一個叫Yuval Harari嘅作者俾大家，樓鼠高度推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424da7857b771f608996c40db687137b53fd878b","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"唔好再睇self help交配書，搵笨的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa4ae908bdeaadd6e45555d4e98d6ee4908490c","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再睇self help交配書，晒錢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dffd908d5b3f54415f0e99b8047065c2fa6a97","tid":2411472,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"啊tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9fb09240cdec3b7ec4ab5f8172098edb1347ad","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔好再睇self help交配書，冇用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2ba6d6a389ddc64c6abf302ee8c3ba26b6020f","tid":2411472,"uid":180302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"想交配就比錢叫雞<br />\n睇乜撚書"},{"pid":"e5d13c84a9c412b92e551c8f6e918aeee2b5a347","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"唔好再睇self help交配書，山埃嚟的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8790ef99f7e63b0a230ebc0d613cf2deed43a8b3","tid":2411472,"uid":21966,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MXHn3e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMXHn3e8.jpg&h=07a11e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇乜用㗎老實講"},{"pid":"2d660a0171d7da5e1232b2fe695755a16a8dbc4c","tid":2411472,"uid":134103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"支持樓主推廣閱讀文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n腹有詩書氣自華，個人有返啲墨水，女女自然來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58342c55fecf476f71b4cdf0add1660987a80cb9","tid":2411472,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q